WWW-Bugzilla3 provides perl bindings for Bugzilla 3.0 API

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc WWW::Bugzilla3

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/WWW-Bugzilla3

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=WWW-Bugzilla3

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/WWW-Bugzilla3

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/WWW-Bugzilla3

